    '{"id":"01KG4ZETFYGT90ZNRYQ2CXT63B","title":"EASE // MiD - Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Product Launch Timeline and Priorities**\n\nThe team committed to launching a new product on **March 1st**, prompting an immediate push to finalize preparations (01:25).\n\n- **Josh Santo confirmed the March 1st launch date**, describing it as a \"small product launch\" but requiring significant last-minute effort.\n- The decision came only **two days prior**, creating a tight timeline and increased workload for the team.\n- This urgency demands focused resource allocation to meet the deadline while managing existing client onboarding.\n- The launch is positioned as a key near-term milestone, with success tied to smooth execution despite the compressed schedule.\n\n## **Podcast Content and Outreach Strategy**\n\nPodcast episodes and outreach campaigns are actively driving engagement and lead generation, with plans to sustain momentum during upcoming absences (02:12).\n\n- **Paula Ocampo reported that the episode with Rajiv is growing steadily** across Buzzsprout, YouTube, and Spotify, indicating rising audience reach (03:15).\n    - The episode is attracting new downloads and plays week over week, enhancing brand visibility.\n- The outreach campaign is scheduled for a **new launch by Monday**, targeting previous contacts who did not respond initially (04:01).\n    - This retargeting effort aims to increase conversion by reconnecting with lukewarm leads.\n- **Josh Santo requested a blog post focused on executive themes related to leadership and manufacturing** during his absence next week, ensuring content continuity (04:20).\n    - Paula agreed to deliver the blog copy by the following week to maintain engagement.\n- Meeting cancellations were planned around team members’ time off, notably **Josh’s absence starting Thursday** and **Paula’s carnival trip**, ensuring workload alignment (05:18).\n\n## **Product Overview Video Development**\n\nThe product overview video is undergoing detailed review with changes planned to improve clarity, flow, and visual support ahead of final release (08:07).\n\n- **Baylee Gunnell initiated a review focused on shortening the video and refining transitions**, though Josh indicated the current length of **3:17 minutes** is acceptable for now (08:36).\n- Specific animation adjustments were requested by Josh to minimize distracting movement and favor subtle effects like typing animation (09:23).\n- Josh clarified that interactive elements like photo-taking buttons should start white and turn blue when selected, improving user interface clarity (09:53).\n- The video sequence will be adjusted so menus and pop-ups appear in a specified order, with certain images replaced by dashboard visuals to better demonstrate reporting features (11:43).\n    - Josh will provide dashboard screenshots, with Baylee’s team open to reusing existing assets to accelerate production.\n- Text corrections and title screen additions were identified, such as adding a missing \"On the Job Training\" title and fixing spelling errors like \"identification\" (14:04).\n- The team agreed to revisit the design stage to refine supporting visuals, including product icons and potential B-roll footage, to enhance storytelling (15:41).\n- Josh suggested recording live video demos to replace some graphical elements, aiming to increase authenticity and viewer understanding (15:59).\n\n## **Budget and Resource Management for Video Production**\n\nBudget concerns were addressed, confirming a fixed-point system that safeguards the project from unexpected cost overruns despite extended editing time (17:09).\n\n- Josh expressed worry about running out of hours or credits to complete the videos without additional budget (17:09).\n- Baylee assured that the last contract was canceled and the current work is under a fixed points arrangement, meaning no extra charges regardless of editing hours used (17:37).\n- This budgeting approach provides financial predictability and allows the team to focus on quality without resource constraints.\n- It ensures ongoing support for podcasts and blog production without risking budget overruns.\n\n## **Team Availability and Scheduling Impacts**\n\nUpcoming team absences require adjustments to meeting schedules and content delivery plans to maintain workflow continuity (05:18).\n\n- Josh will be off from Thursday through Tuesday, returning Wednesday, which affects scheduling for the week of the 18th (05:23).\n- Paula will be out attending a carnival, impacting availability during the same time frame (05:30).\n- Baylee confirmed awareness of these absences and coordinated cancellations accordingly.\n- Planning includes producing additional content like blogs during these gaps to keep audience engagement steady.","outline":null,"keywords":["Product Launch","Podcast Updates","Outreach Campaign","Video Production","Budget Management","Time Off Scheduling"],"overview":"- **Product Launch Date:** New product launching on March 1st requires immediate final preparations and resource allocation.  \n- **Podcast Engagement:** Episode with Rajiv is gaining traction, enhancing brand visibility through Buzzsprout, YouTube, and Spotify.  \n- **Outreach Strategy:** New retargeting campaign launching Monday aims to reconnect with past lukewarm leads for better conversions.  \n- **Video Development Review:** Focus on shortening product overview video while refining transitions and improving clarity before final release.  \n- **Budget Security:** Fixed-point system safeguards video production budget, allowing for quality focus without unexpected cost overruns.  \n- **Team Absences Impact:** Upcoming absences of team members require adjustments in meeting schedules and content delivery planning.","action_items":"\n**Paula Ocampo**\nShare podcast episode images and blog post by Friday (02:12)\nPrepare new outreach campaign and aim to have it ready by Monday for launch and retargeting (03:52)\nDraft executive-themed blog post for Josh’s week off and share copy by next week (04:20)\nCoordinate meeting scheduling and cancellations for planned time off (Josh’s and Paula’s absences) (05:18)\nReview and implement corrections and revisions for the product overview video based on discussion, including transition and visual flow adjustments (08:07)\nClarify supporting visuals requirements with the design team and integrate demo videos as needed (15:41)\n\n**Josh Santo**\nProvide dashboard visuals or allow reuse from other scenes for video edits (12:30)\nConfirm and deliver any demo video recordings to assist with product overview video enhancements (15:41)\n\n**Baylee Gunnell**\nManage communication and execution of video production updates including cuts, transitions, animations, and spelling corrections (08:07)\nEnsure proper conveyance of Josh’s feedback to the video editing team (15:31)\nReassure Josh about budget and point allocation and maintain updated point tracking for ongoing content work (17:09)\n"},"duration":19.1200008392334,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Josh Santo"},{"id":1,"name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"id":2,"name":"Baylee Gunnell"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hey.","index":0,"end_time":9.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":9.28,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Hey, Bailey.","index":1,"end_time":18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":17.28,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Can you hear me?","index":2,"end_time":18.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":18,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":3,"end_time":19.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":19.12,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Great.","index":4,"end_time":20.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":20.56,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"How you doing?","index":5,"end_time":24.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":23.28,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Doing.","index":6,"end_time":26.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":26.01,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Doing great.","index":7,"end_time":27.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":26.49,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We just had a upsell conversation with another client.","index":8,"end_time":32.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":27.69,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Went really well.","index":9,"end_time":32.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":32.01,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So.","index":10,"end_time":33.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":33.13,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":11,"end_time":34.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":34.09,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Exciting stuff.","index":12,"end_time":36.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":35.29,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, awesome.","index":13,"end_time":40.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":37.61,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, I saw Justin message screen.","index":14,"end_time":44.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":40.13,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":15,"end_time":45.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":44.97,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Good stuff going on.","index":16,"end_time":46.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":45.45,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"This meeting is being recorded.","index":17,"end_time":49.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":47.37,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Hey, Josh.","index":18,"end_time":51.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":50.97,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Hey, y''.","index":19,"end_time":52.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.13,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"All.","index":20,"end_time":52.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":52.41,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":21,"end_time":55.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":54.29,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Great.","index":22,"end_time":56.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":55.97,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"How about you?","index":23,"end_time":57.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":57.01,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Those are okay.","index":24,"end_time":60.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":60.05,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"It''s busy.","index":25,"end_time":61.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":60.93,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I know.","index":26,"end_time":63.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":62.61,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"It''s been a crazy week for all of us, I think.","index":27,"end_time":65.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":63.25,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":28,"end_time":67.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":66.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":29,"end_time":69.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":69.09,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Anything in particular keeping you really busy right now, Josh?","index":30,"end_time":72.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":69.49,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":31,"end_time":74.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":74.05,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"We''re going to launch a new product.","index":32,"end_time":77.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":74.61,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"There''s a lot of stuff with that going on.","index":33,"end_time":79.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":77.09,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s always a lot of work.","index":34,"end_time":84.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":80.94,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":35,"end_time":85.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":84.78,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Because we just decided like two days ago that March 1st was the day, and so it''s a scramble now.","index":36,"end_time":92.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":85.82,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s crazy.","index":37,"end_time":95.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":93.9,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It''s going to be a small product launch, though, but still a lot to do.","index":38,"end_time":99.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":96.06,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, a lot.","index":39,"end_time":103.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":102.7,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Lot to prepare there.","index":40,"end_time":104.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":103.42,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":41,"end_time":105.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":105.27,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"What about on your side?","index":42,"end_time":107.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":106.23,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, we just got, I think, a few new clients, so always gotta shuffle around a few things there to.","index":43,"end_time":117.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":109.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"To get them.","index":44,"end_time":119.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":118.23,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"To get them going, but always a good problem to have.","index":45,"end_time":123.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":119.75,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So.","index":46,"end_time":124.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":124.23,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, always happy to.","index":47,"end_time":126.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":124.63,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"To be working with more people.","index":48,"end_time":128.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":126.87,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Great.","index":49,"end_time":130.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":129.91,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Great.","index":50,"end_time":132.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":132.72,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So I''m going to share my screen and we can go over what we have today.","index":51,"end_time":140.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":133.52,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":52,"end_time":149.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":148.88,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So for today, we have some podcast updates.","index":53,"end_time":154.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":149.76,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Also I want to share some podcast stats as well.","index":54,"end_time":158.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":154.64,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Also we have some updates of the outreach campaign, the retargeting campaign we''re working on.","index":55,"end_time":163.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":158.49,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"And also we want to go through the product of review video with you to review your comments and everything.","index":56,"end_time":172.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":164.41,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So we''ll start with some podcast updates.","index":57,"end_time":176.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":172.41,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"The episode with Ann is in progress.","index":58,"end_time":179.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":176.81,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Thank you so much for sharing the title.","index":59,"end_time":181.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":179.13,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"We''re working on the images and we''ll have everything ready by Friday along with the blog post.","index":60,"end_time":188.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":181.25,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Great.","index":61,"end_time":192.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":192.53,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Now moving into some podcast stats.","index":62,"end_time":196.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":193.65,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"The episode with Rajiv keeps growing week over week.","index":63,"end_time":201.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":197.49,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So we have new downloads from Buzzsprout, also new views from YouTube and new plays from Spotify.","index":64,"end_time":208.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":201.89,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"And they want from Julie Atkins.","index":65,"end_time":213.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":210.07,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I got some new plays from Spotify, which is great to see as well.","index":66,"end_time":217.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":213.67,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"And then for the outreach campaign, I wanted to ask you if someone else scheduled a time with you from the previous campaign.","index":67,"end_time":230.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":222.63,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"No, no, I talked with one person, but that was from the.","index":68,"end_time":237.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":232.47,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"We''d already talked about how he had scheduled, but that''s it.","index":69,"end_time":241.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":237.76,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":70,"end_time":242.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":241.6,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So we will try to have the new campaign ready by this week.","index":71,"end_time":246.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":242.56,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So try to have it ready by Monday so we can launch it by then and start retargeting those people that probably.","index":72,"end_time":255.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":246.96,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"We connected with them before but didn''t get back to us.","index":73,"end_time":258.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":255.16,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":74,"end_time":260.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":260,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m taking some time off next week, so I doubt that we''re going to have another episode by that time, so.","index":75,"end_time":274.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":262.32,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Wondering if we could do another blog post like we''ve done before?","index":76,"end_time":278.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":274.92,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, for sure.","index":77,"end_time":280.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":279.48,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"We can come put together another blog for that week.","index":78,"end_time":284.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":280.52,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, that works.","index":79,"end_time":286.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":284.84,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I think we''ve talked with a couple of executives in the podcast.","index":80,"end_time":290.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":286.6,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Maybe it can be something, because I''m trying to think of something that would be appealing to executives.","index":81,"end_time":298.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":292.71,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So maybe there''s some sort of themes between executive leadership and manufacturing.","index":82,"end_time":304.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":298.79,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":83,"end_time":306.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":305.67,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, that makes sense.","index":84,"end_time":307.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":306.39,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Thoroughly.","index":85,"end_time":307.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":307.35,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay, that''s great.","index":86,"end_time":309.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":307.91,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So we''ll start working on that and I''ll share copy and everything probably by next week.","index":87,"end_time":315.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":309.59,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":88,"end_time":318.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":317.9,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Do we need to cancel the meeting for next week if you''re gonna be out?","index":89,"end_time":321.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":318.38,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I will be out starting Thursday, so I won''t be here.","index":90,"end_time":326.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":323.18,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":91,"end_time":328.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":326.86,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Paula''s gonna be out too.","index":92,"end_time":329.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":328.58,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":93,"end_time":331.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":330.46,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Are you going somewhere?","index":94,"end_time":333.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":332.06,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m going to a different city to a carnival with my friends.","index":95,"end_time":337.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":333.9,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Oh, cool.","index":96,"end_time":337.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":337.06,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s my first time in a carnival, so.","index":97,"end_time":340.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":338.22,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Oh, cool.","index":98,"end_time":341.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":340.66,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Really excited?","index":99,"end_time":341.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":341.26,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yes.","index":100,"end_time":342.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":342.3,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":101,"end_time":343.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":343.48,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"What about you, Josh?","index":102,"end_time":344.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":343.68,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Are you doing anything fun?","index":103,"end_time":345.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":344.52,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Going to Hawaii.","index":104,"end_time":347.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":346.12,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Oh, you''re kidding.","index":105,"end_time":349.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":347.96,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''ve never been.","index":106,"end_time":350.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":349.96,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Really?","index":107,"end_time":351.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":351.24,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":108,"end_time":352.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":352.12,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Which island are you going to?","index":109,"end_time":354.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":352.76,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"The main one.","index":110,"end_time":357.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":357,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Is that.","index":111,"end_time":359.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":359.16,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Isn''t that Hawaii?","index":112,"end_time":361.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":360.04,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Hawaii?","index":113,"end_time":362.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":361.6,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":114,"end_time":362.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":362.2,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like the Big island or Oahu?","index":115,"end_time":365.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":362.48,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yes.","index":116,"end_time":368.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":367.72,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yep.","index":117,"end_time":368.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":368.53,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Oahu.","index":118,"end_time":369.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":368.77,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That''s gonna be so nice.","index":119,"end_time":372.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":371.25,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"How long are you gonna be gone?","index":120,"end_time":374.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":372.93,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"A couple days.","index":121,"end_time":376.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":375.17,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So we''ll get there Thursday and fly back Tuesday, but we won''t get home till Wednesday.","index":122,"end_time":382.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":376.53,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That''s so nice.","index":123,"end_time":385.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":384.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, so, so nice.","index":124,"end_time":387.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":385.81,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s.","index":125,"end_time":388.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":387.81,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"My dad goes every year for a work engagement and it''s like a two to three week long thing because he does a lot of training, so he''s teaching classes and stuff over there.","index":126,"end_time":400.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":388.37,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And for the past couple of years, I''m like, oh my God, you''re going to Hawaii.","index":127,"end_time":404.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":400.79,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"All expense paid for almost a month.","index":128,"end_time":407.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":404.43,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Are you having fun?","index":129,"end_time":409.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":408.27,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"What does your dad do?","index":130,"end_time":410.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":409.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"How can I do what your dad does?","index":131,"end_time":412.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":410.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"He''s in law enforcement, so he trains police.","index":132,"end_time":416.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":413.79,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Police forces.","index":133,"end_time":417.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":417.23,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And he runs like a police academy here in Texas.","index":134,"end_time":421.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":417.91,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So he goes and he trains the police out there.","index":135,"end_time":425.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":422.44,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Oh, that''s so cool.","index":136,"end_time":427.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":426.36,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":137,"end_time":428.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":428.04,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"But I always ask him like, do you have a good time?","index":138,"end_time":431.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":429,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And he''s like, no.","index":139,"end_time":433.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":431.84,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So this time decided, we''re gonna go and have a good time with him.","index":140,"end_time":442.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":438.2,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That''s awesome.","index":141,"end_time":444.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":444.12,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m sure.","index":142,"end_time":445.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":445.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, that''d be lonely.","index":143,"end_time":447.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":446.04,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"You''re just by yourself, so be nice to have you out there with him.","index":144,"end_time":451,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":447.28,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":145,"end_time":453.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":452.62,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I think that''s fine.","index":146,"end_time":454.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":453.42,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That''s so nice.","index":147,"end_time":455.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":454.86,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"I think I saw you cancel the meeting for the 18th, so that''s probably the.","index":148,"end_time":460.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":455.74,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"That you coming back, I believe.","index":149,"end_time":463.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":460.34,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So your cancellation for that week.","index":150,"end_time":465.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":463.02,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":151,"end_time":468.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":467.98,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"On the.","index":152,"end_time":468.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":468.34,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Oh.","index":153,"end_time":469.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":469.26,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Oh, oh, yeah.","index":154,"end_time":470.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":469.66,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"On the 18th.","index":155,"end_time":471.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":470.58,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yes.","index":156,"end_time":472.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":471.7,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yes, you''re right.","index":157,"end_time":473.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":472.3,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":158,"end_time":473.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":473.1,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yes.","index":159,"end_time":473.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":473.46,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":160,"end_time":475.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":474.78,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And yeah, then the last thing is to go through the product overview video.","index":161,"end_time":483.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":478.07,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"So, Bailey, I don''t know if you want to share the screen, we can go over there.","index":162,"end_time":487.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":483.35,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, we just had a few questions based on the comments on there.","index":163,"end_time":492.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":487.91,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So I''ll just share my screen and we can go through them.","index":164,"end_time":495.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":493.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So first off, I had left a couple comments about some areas we could potentially cut out if you wanted.","index":165,"end_time":503.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":497.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And it''s totally optional.","index":166,"end_time":505.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":503.91,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I know.","index":167,"end_time":505.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":505.43,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We were just talking about, like, how can we shorten these videos?","index":168,"end_time":508.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":505.83,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So I wasn''t sure if you wanted to cut some stuff out or keep it as is.","index":169,"end_time":513.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":508.43,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, it''s 317 is a good length.","index":170,"end_time":521.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":516.07,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"If that''s the video right now.","index":171,"end_time":523.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":521.27,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":172,"end_time":523.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":523.51,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, then we''ll just ignore those for now.","index":173,"end_time":526.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":523.91,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But I''m still open to cuts.","index":174,"end_time":529.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":527.59,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Like, that''s not a no.","index":175,"end_time":529.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":529.27,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"That''s just.","index":176,"end_time":530.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":529.99,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":177,"end_time":531.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":530.55,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, for now.","index":178,"end_time":532.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":531.68,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We can keep it then.","index":179,"end_time":533.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":532.2,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then my next.","index":180,"end_time":537.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":534.24,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"These all made sense.","index":181,"end_time":540.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":538.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"This all made sense.","index":182,"end_time":544.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":543.52,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":183,"end_time":546.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":545.36,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"This is where I started to have some questions.","index":184,"end_time":547.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":546.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So you said no movement.","index":185,"end_time":549.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":547.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m guessing there''s kind of, like, how it''s moving around.","index":186,"end_time":553.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":549.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Is that what the movement we need to get rid of?","index":187,"end_time":555.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":553.6,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, so just let me add a comment.","index":188,"end_time":558.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":555.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So, like, the transitions in and out.","index":189,"end_time":563.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":559.86,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Should stay, but we.","index":190,"end_time":566.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":563.86,"speaker_name":"Paula Ocampo"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s like the bobbing and.","index":191,"end_time":572.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":570.66,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":192,"end_time":573.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":572.82,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So anytime I wrote no movement, it''s.","index":193,"end_time":576.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":574.82,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"It''s okay.","index":194,"end_time":577.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":576.54,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I just want to make sure our team totally understands if it''ll.","index":195,"end_time":582.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":577.98,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":196,"end_time":583.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":582.67,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then this was another one I was a little confused on is to have a Yes.","index":197,"end_time":590.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":584.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I think it was for this to take the photo.","index":198,"end_time":593.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":591.07,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Oh, you were at the right one.","index":199,"end_time":596.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":593.95,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":200,"end_time":597.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":597.15,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":201,"end_time":597.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":597.51,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So right now, I think they all pop up at the same time.","index":202,"end_time":603.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":597.83,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"I think that''s fine.","index":203,"end_time":605.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":604.67,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"But I. I would like to.","index":204,"end_time":606.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":605.63,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Instead of it being blue by default, it pops up like the other ones and then blue as if it''s being selected.","index":205,"end_time":614.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":608.28,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":206,"end_time":616.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":615.32,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So it starts off white.","index":207,"end_time":617.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":616.32,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":208,"end_time":619.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":618.68,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":209,"end_ti