ker_id":2,"start_time":681.82,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So it''s like, you''ll see it''s right after that.","index":225,"end_time":687.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":684.14,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":226,"end_time":688.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":687.94,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"You''ll see that you hit fail.","index":227,"end_time":689.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":688.34,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And when you hit fail, it''s like, like the menu popping up to be like.","index":228,"end_time":693.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":689.54,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And there will be a specific order.","index":229,"end_time":695.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":693.94,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"You know, it''ll be like a one, two kind of thing.","index":230,"end_time":698.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":696.1,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And then go to the next scene that has the.","index":231,"end_time":701.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":698.78,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"The visual.","index":232,"end_time":702.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":702.02,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":233,"end_time":704.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":703.62,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So these two should pop up with the phone screen.","index":234,"end_time":708.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":704.26,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":235,"end_time":709.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":709.54,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And it would be the top one first.","index":236,"end_time":713.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":709.9,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":237,"end_time":715.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":715.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So this one transitions in first, then this one.","index":238,"end_time":718.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":716.03,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":239,"end_time":719.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":719.31,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And then should these fade away with that phone screen?","index":240,"end_time":723.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":720.11,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then this is just by itself.","index":241,"end_time":725.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":723.67,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":242,"end_time":728.029,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":727.39,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Like we wouldn''t have this here.","index":243,"end_time":729.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":728.029,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And then I''d want to keep this image but add an image of a dashboard.","index":244,"end_time":738.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":729.63,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And so like this one on the right would be a little bit smaller and kind of take the place where these two are on the left right now.","index":245,"end_time":746.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":738.98,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"And then we get a dashboard one that shows.","index":246,"end_time":749.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":746.42,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So then we''re showing like the reports and stuff.","index":247,"end_time":752.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":750.34,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"So just seeing if that''s on here because we don''t think.","index":248,"end_time":759.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":753.38,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Do we have one for the dashboards?","index":249,"end_time":762.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":760.1,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"No, but I can send you.","index":250,"end_time":764.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":762.98,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay.","index":251,"end_time":764.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":764.18,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Right now, I mean, we have dashboards for other.","index":252,"end_t