as part of that same comment that we just talked through.","index":267,"end_time":804.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":801.83,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then this, this is more just talking about like how they''re transitioning together.","index":268,"end_time":811.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":807.19,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like it shouldn''t be like swiping or.","index":269,"end_time":813.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":811.51,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Right.","index":270,"end_time":814.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":814.23,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"It should just look like they''re clicking.","index":271,"end_time":816.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":814.55,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":272,"end_time":818.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":817.67,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It''s almost like no animation or if there was animation, ideally it would look like it was being typed, if anything.","index":273,"end_time":826.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":819.11,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":274,"end_time":827.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":826.5,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we can use those recordings you made to see how that all.","index":275,"end_time":831.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":827.9,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"All looks.","index":276,"end_time":832.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":831.54,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then what.","index":277,"end_time":837.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":835.54,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I mean, this is another one I''m a little confused about.","index":278,"end_time":840.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":837.78,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, is it like the text in here?","index":279,"end_time":844.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":842.5,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"No.","index":280,"end_time":845.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_tim