ur hour, if our team spends hundreds of hours editing you don''t get charged anything extra because we''re just using points for it.","index":331,"end_time":1085.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1076.02,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So budget wise, that''s not going to change anything there.","index":332,"end_time":1089.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1086.12,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Right now, we''ve already allocated the points you need towards it, so that''s not going to change.","index":333,"end_time":1094.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1089.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And you''ll just keep getting the points you need for the podcast and the blogs.","index":334,"end_time":1097.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1094.36,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":335,"end_time":1098.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1098.04,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":336,"end_time":1099.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1098.68,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, I was a little concerned that, you know, it''s just taking longer than I think we anticipated and we don''t have any more money to throw at it.","index":337,"end_time":1108.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1099.4,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, no, yeah, you''re all taken care of there.","index":338,"end_time":1113.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1109,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":339,"end_time":1116.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1113.97,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":340,"end_time":1118.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1118.29,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, thank you for chatting and we''ll be in touch.","index":341,"end_time":1121.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1118.77,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, thank you.","index":342,"end_time":1122.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1121.81,"speaker_name":"Josh Santo"},{"text":"Thank you.","index"