  VALUES (
    '6a9f190a-9e44-4b24-8f1d-d82022950bb9',
    '2026-01-29 13:30:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KFK1D0436H77DBCEGTK3N6R7',
    'Agrippon // New North Weekly Connect',
    '{"Keenan Toward","Nathalie Mintjens","Shane Billings"}'::text[],
    1292,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83663022990?pwd=R1aTMdTGv2yblYfzlB6Wv1Sup4Z47U.1',
    '{"id":"01KFK1D0436H77DBCEGTK3N6R7","title":"Agrippon // New North Weekly Connect","summary":{"notes":"## **Lead Generation and Outreach Performance**\n\nLead generation via LinkedIn is growing rapidly, with outreach efforts focused on qualifying and engaging potential clients.\n\n- **LinkedIn connection requests increased to 29 this week**, a **300% rise from 8 last week**, signaling strong new lead flow (02:00)  \n    - Keenan is selectively following up on those who replied and filtering by role to prioritize quality conversations  \n    - Shane noted it often takes multiple touch points on LinkedIn before engagement occurs, supporting a patient outreach approach  \n    - Automated LinkedIn messaging sequences from Brad reduce manual workload, continuing follow-ups until prospects respond  \n    - Keenan plans to call leads who submitted forms but did not respond, targeting early morning hours for better contact rates  \n\n- **LinkedIn metrics reveal a 24% acceptance rate for billing organizations and 67% message reply rate on those connections**, while DSOs show lower engagement at 15% acceptance and 26% reply rates (08:29)  \n    - Keenan questioned the 67% reply rate, finding only 7 replies out of 38 connections, suggesting data may be skewed or segmented differently  \n    - Nathalie confirmed all replies appear in LinkedIn’s message section, indicating Keenan’s view might be limited to certain subsets  \n    - Shane highlighted some promising prospects familiar with the company’s products, like Zanetta from E Assist, who may be valuable targets  \n\n## **Email Campaigns and Website Engagement**\n\nRenewed focus on email campaigns and website optimization is critical as organic engagement trends downward.\n\n- **Website visits and email clicks are declining**, emphasizing the need to launch new ABM campaigns quickly to sustain traffic and lead flow (13:50)  \n    - Historically, ABM campaigns have driven the largest share of website visits, so delays risk further traffic drops  \n    - Nathalie shared updated outreach email sequences for DSOs and billing companies, awaiting Keenan’s feedback for launch  \n    - January’s click data will be analyzed on January 31 to create a targeted list of prospects with 3+ clicks for lower-funnel nurture emails from Keenan  \n\n- **Forms on the website and LinkedIn ads now require phone numbers**, improving lead quality and enabling better follow-up (14:58)  \n    - This change supports more direct engagement efforts and helps prioritize leads with confirmed contact info  \n\n## **Product and Feature Development**\n\nProduct updates focus on improving onboarding and internal task management to enhance client experience and operational efficiency.\n\n- **Tiered onboarding feature development is complete, with pull requests merged and live updates across key website pages** (13:51)  \n    - This includes guided onboarding messaging prominently placed on homepage and about page to set clear expectations  \n    - Shane emphasized the team will lead launches and stay involved to ensure smooth adoption and customer success  \n\n- **Upcoming internal tasking feature will allow team members to assign tasks within their own departments**, shifting from cross-team tasking only (17:30)  \n    - Shane plans to release this within 1–2 weeks and will monitor adoption and feedback to guide further improvements  \n\n- **Online self-signup with credit card payment is under consideration, requiring close collaboration between Shane and Keenan to set pricing and process details** (18:10)  \n    - The feature will offer fixed pricing with no discounts online; volume discounts will require direct sales engagement  \n    - Keenan suggested integrating scheduling so new signups can be onboarded promptly, potentially on Fridays when he is available  \n    - This development is expected to take a couple of months, emphasizing the need for strategic planning  \n\n## **Process Improvements and Operational Planning**\n\nOperational adjustments aim to balance automation with targeted manual engagement to maximize efficiency without losing personalization.\n\n- Keenan is experimenting with selective manual follow-ups on LinkedIn to gauge conversation quality before relying fully on automation (04:48)  \n    - He plans to respond only to promising leads or those who reply, letting automated sequences handle the rest  \n    - Shane recommended calling leads who fill forms but don’t answer messages, adjusting outreach timing based on time zones for better results (06:33)  \n\n- Nathalie confirmed automated LinkedIn follow-ups continue until prospects respond, reducing Keenan’s messaging load (04:11)  \n    - This system ensures persistent contact attempts without overburdening the outreach lead  \n    - Keenan will review and approve updated email sequences today to accelerate campaign launches (20:50)  \n\n## **Strategic Priorities and Next Steps**\n\nThe team is aligned on prioritizing lead nurturing via ABM campaigns and developing scalable onboarding and signup features to drive growth.\n\n- Rapid approval and deployment of updated outreach emails is essential to reverse declining website traffic and maintain pipeline velocity (13:50)  \n    - Keenan has time today to review sequences and will coordinate with Shane to finalize launch timing (20:50)  \n\n- Product leadership sees online self-registration as a strategic growth lever but stresses the need to set clear pricing and onboarding workflows first (18:10)  \n    - Close collaboration between Keenan and Shane is planned to define process and timeline for this multi-month development  \n\n- Internal tasking improvements will enhance team efficiency and accountability, with initial rollout planned within the next two weeks (17:30)  \n    - Monitoring adoption and feedback will inform further refinements to support operational scale  \n\n- The team is leveraging detailed LinkedIn engagement data and website analytics to continuously refine targeting and messaging strategies for DSOs and billing organizations (08:29)  \n    - Focusing on leads with multiple website interactions aims to improve conversion rates and sales efficiency by prioritizing warmer prospects","outline":null,"keywords":["LinkedIn outreach","ABM campaigns","onboarding support","lead follow-up","website updates","internal tasking"],"overview":"- **Lead Generation Boost:** LinkedIn connection requests rose to 29 this week, a 300% increase from 8 last week.  \n- **Email Campaigns Urgent:** Decline in website visits and email clicks signals need for new ABM campaigns to maintain lead flow.  \n- **Onboarding Enhancements Live:** Tiered onboarding feature now active, improving user experience with clear guided messaging on pages.  \n- **Tasking Feature Launch Soon:** New internal tasking feature expected within 1–2 weeks to boost departmental efficiency.  \n- **Self-Signup Development:** Online signup with fixed pricing being considered, emphasizing collaboration on pricing and onboarding details.  \n- **Data-Driven Targeting:** Analyzing LinkedIn and website engagement to refine communication strategies for better client conversion.","action_items":"\n**Keenan Toward**\nReview updated outreach email sequences for DSOs and billing companies and provide feedback (07:58)\nFollow up with LinkedIn contacts who have responded and selectively engage others based on role and company fit (13:37)\nConduct early morning calls to leads who submitted forms but have not responded to messages, taking into account their possible time zones (06:33)\nInvestigate the discrepancy in LinkedIn reply rates compared to actual message replies seen (09:14)\nCoordinate with Shane to strategize the upcoming online sign-up feature, deciding on pricing and onboarding support implications (18:23)\nReview and approve email outreach sequences immediately after the meeting to enable campaign launch (20:30)\n\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nSend Keenan the updated outreach sequences after the meeting for review (15:40)\nPrioritize launching new ABM email campaigns once the sequences are approved (13:58)\nProvide Keenan with a list of people with three or more website clicks for January analysis, to be used in lower funnel nurturing (08:29)\nFollow up on LinkedIn ads and website form updates requiring phone numbers to improve lead quality (14:58)\n\n**Shane Billings**\nMerge marketing updates and pull requests related to website and onboarding content (14:52)\nDiscuss online sign-up pricing and registration workflows with Keenan post-meeting (18:23)\nMonitor reception of the new internal tasking feature after launch and measure usage for billing and office teams separately (17:26)\n"},"duration":21.540000915527344,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Keenan Toward"},{"id":1,"name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"id":2,"name":"Shane Billings"}],"sentences":[{"text":"And so the commerce.","index":0,"end_time":1.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.8,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"The three that I''ve actually communicated with, had conversations with, haven''t technically been potential clients.","index":1,"end_time":8.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1.76,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So.","index":2,"end_time":11.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":10.72,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But I''ll kind of go over that a little bit more.","index":3,"end_time":13.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":11.84,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay.","index":4,"end_time":16.399,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":15.84,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"See if Shane''s jumping on here.","index":5,"end_time":20.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":18.48,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah, Shane''s here.","index":6,"end_time":22.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":21.6,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, he is?","index":7,"end_time":23.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":22.96,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":8,"end_time":24.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":23.6,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I''m kind of pulling double duty.","index":9,"end_time":25.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":24.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''m on.","index":10,"end_time":26.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":25.84,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, well, then I''ll go ahead and go through it a little bit.","index":11,"end_time":30.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":28.93,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Natalie, let me.","index":12,"end_time":35.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":31.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''m gonna share real quick.","index":13,"end_time":43.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":41.17,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay.","index":14,"end_time":44.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":43.57,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"See if I can.","index":15,"end_time":58.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":57.66,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":16,"end_time":61.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.34,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So you see the spreadsheet I have up?","index":17,"end_time":63.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":61.7,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yep.","index":18,"end_time":64.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":63.82,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So what I''m doing in here is kind of documenting for myself kind of what the lead source was, who they are, what company they''re with, you know, phone numbers, if we have them, locations, just any of the details, it could be pertinent to conversation.","index":19,"end_time":80.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":65.26,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So if you look at a few of these, like, Amber is a.","index":20,"end_time":86.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":82.87,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"She''s a current client from E Assist, so we''re actually getting her started on our own.","index":21,"end_time":92.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":86.75,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"On the second, Sandy sent a request, but she didn''t answer her phone and hasn''t responded to the message yet either.","index":22,"end_time":102.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":93.67,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Those are the two forms that I''m currently working on.","index":23,"end_time":105.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":102.71,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And then as far as our LinkedIn, we had eight last week.","index":24,"end_time":110.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":106.88,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I have 29 this week.","index":25,"end_time":112.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":110.64,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So I''ll try to respond to all of those between today and tomorrow to get some conversations going.","index":26,"end_time":120.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":112.4,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But I had conversations with three.","index":27,"end_time":122.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":120.32,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Three people.","index":28,"end_time":122.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":122.24,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So one, Alexander works with public schools, so he''s just basically had a conversation about his education in school and, you know, what his.","index":29,"end_time":134.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":124.32,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"What his focus is there.","index":30,"end_time":136.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":134.66,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And then.","index":31,"end_time":137.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":137.3,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Vishaka is she''s actually doesn''t have a job, but she wants a demo.","index":32,"end_time":144.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":139.86,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So I''m gonna follow up with her and.","index":33,"end_time":146.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":144.66,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And see, you know, what the potential is.","index":34,"end_time":149.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":147.22,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And if that''s something that.","index":35,"end_time":151.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":149.74,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"That we can utilize for, maybe she can point us in the direction of other potential clients.","index":36,"end_time":158.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":151.46,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And then I had one other gentleman reach out on LinkedIn that I haven''t responded to yet.","index":37,"end_time":165.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":160.23,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And those are not loaded on here yet because I haven''t responded.","index":38,"end_time":168.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":165.43,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But his conversation, essentially he''s open to work.","index":39,"end_time":171.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":168.79,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So I kind of put the OTW for open to work.","index":40,"end_time":173.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":171.27,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And so I''ll share this with you guys just to kind of understand what kind of connections we''re getting.","index":41,"end_time":179.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":174.15,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And then, you know, hopefully we can.","index":42,"end_time":184.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":181.59,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"We can continue to.","index":43,"end_time":186.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":185.2,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"To grow this.","index":44,"end_time":187.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":186.56,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But 29 this week, obviously that''s 30% up from last.","index":45,"end_time":192.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":187.44,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Last week, so.","index":46,"end_time":193.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":192.48,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Or three times 300% up.","index":47,"end_time":196.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":194.32,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So that''s.","index":48,"end_time":196.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":196.04,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"That''s good opportunity and connection.","index":49,"end_time":200.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":198.56,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So I''ll respond to those and see what we get out of it.","index":50,"end_time":202.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":200.16,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":51,"end_time":203.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":203.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Are those people that have sent you a message or just people that accepted our connection request?","index":52,"end_time":208.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":203.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Most of them have just sent us a connection request.","index":53,"end_time":211.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":209.36,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"A couple have responded and like one response was, I''m no in a dental office.","index":54,"end_time":217.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":212,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I''m in rcm.","index":55,"end_time":218.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":217.66,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Or sometimes they share something like that, or sometimes they respond more specifically to Brad''s background than they do the grip on items that we''re sending them.","index":56,"end_time":231.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":219.26,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"They''re wanting to connect with Brad specifically.","index":57,"end_time":233.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":231.82,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So.","index":58,"end_time":234.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":234.06,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And in some of those conversations, you know, I try to guide the conversation along as a grip on is as one of the projects that he''s working on.","index":59,"end_time":243.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":235.98,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And that''s kind of the discussion that Brad and I had.","index":60,"end_time":245.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":243.6,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And so that''s kind of how I''m utilizing the information at this point.","index":61,"end_time":250.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":246.6,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay.","index":62,"end_time":251.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":251.16,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The way we have it set up is that so when we send someone a connection request, they accept it.","index":63,"end_time":257.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":252.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We actually have the messages going out automatically from Brad so that you''re not spending too much time doing that manually.","index":64,"end_time":266.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":258.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So like you said, that''s like 30 people that you''d have to message manually.","index":65,"end_time":270.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":266.84,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"If you don''t message them, it''s just going to keep sending automated sequences until they respond.","index":66,"end_time":276.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":271.51,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Then that''s when our automation stops and then you can jump in.","index":67,"end_time":280.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":277.03,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So if that''s easier for you, you don''t have to follow up with everybody manually.","index":68,"end_time":285.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":281.03,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It''s just going to keep sending automated messages.","index":69,"end_time":287.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":285.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, no, that''s great.","index":70,"end_time":290.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":288.07,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I wanted to reach out to some people to initially kind of gauge what kind of conversation I could drive and if I could get some responses, get people to go to the website or engage them in conversation.","index":71,"end_time":301.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":290.19,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But yeah, to this point it hasn''t been overly fruitful.","index":72,"end_time":307.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":302.4,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So, you know, Shane and I had the conversation about how many touch points it takes on LinkedIn before you get responses from people or engage them.","index":73,"end_time":314.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":307.76,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And so I might allow these.","index":74,"end_time":317.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":314.72,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Some of these.","index":75,"end_time":318.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":317.84,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I''ll probably respond to some of the 29 and not all of the 29 and then see how the communications play out.","index":76,"end_time":325.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":318.72,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I have seen the second string for.","index":77,"end_time":327.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":325.85,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"There''s nine people this morning where the second string of communication took place.","index":78,"end_time":332.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":327.81,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And it says, hey, following up.","index":79,"end_time":334.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":332.49,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"You know, I wanted to follow up again is the second message from LinkedIn.","index":80,"end_time":338.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":334.25,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And so anybody who''s sent something back, I''m trying to respond to for sure.","index":81,"end_time":344.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":339.37,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And then I pick out some people based on their role within organizations or what their organization is to try to engage them as well.","index":82,"end_time":352.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":345.05,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But I''ll probably let a string of those play out with, with your marketing communications and See what happens there.","index":83,"end_time":359.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":352.09,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay, so.","index":84,"end_time":361.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":359.82,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But I''ll stop sharing and I''ll let you give us the update.","index":85,"end_time":365.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":361.82,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Hold on real quick.","index":86,"end_time":366.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":365.42,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So the two that aren''t responding that filled out the forms, I think those are the most surprising.","index":87,"end_time":370.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":366.26,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Well, the one, the one that filled out the form did respond, but she doesn''t have a job.","index":88,"end_time":375.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":371.9,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":89,"end_time":376.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":376.06,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, but there was a second one.","index":90,"end_time":378.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":376.78,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That was it.","index":91,"end_time":379.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":378.3,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":92,"end_time":379.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":379.31,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And.","index":93,"end_time":381.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":381.11,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And I''ve learned at this point, anytime I''ve got a response from somebody, it''s when it''s like seven o'' clock in the morning.","index":94,"end_time":386.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":381.43,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"They''re probably in the office getting started for their day and it hasn''t gotten busy yet, or they''ve been in the evening.","index":95,"end_time":392.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":386.43,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I wonder if you can call them at that time because you have their phone number or the one that.","index":96,"end_time":398.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":393.27,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, she didn''t answer her phone number either.","index":97,"end_time":401.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":400.07,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So I''m not sure what the engagement was in getting the form submitted, but.","index":98,"end_time":408.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":403.27,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But yeah, she didn''t answer her phone either, so.","index":99,"end_time":411.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":409.27,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And I don''t know what time their office is closed.","index":100,"end_time":413.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":411.91,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So I might do a little bit more research on that.","index":101,"end_time":415.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":413.75,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But I''ll probably try to call her this morning after our call, probably between seven and eight, to see if I can catch her before her day has started.","index":102,"end_time":423.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":415.55,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But that also depends on what her location is.","index":103,"end_time":427.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":424.709,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So now I''ve got to see what her time zone is because she may be east or west or wherever that may be.","index":104,"end_time":433.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":427.11,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So I''ll follow up on any of the ones with the phone number.","index":105,"end_time":436.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":433.35,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I''ll call again today or tomorrow.","index":106,"end_time":439.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":436.55,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay.","index":107,"end_time":444.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":443.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"All right, Natalie, take it away.","index":108,"end_time":451.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":449.48,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":109,"end_time":453.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":452.76,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, so I had the.","index":110,"end_time":454.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":453.36,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, the list here just to go over where some of these leads stand.","index":111,"end_time":458.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":454.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So the one from the free trial, she''s not answering either?","index":112,"end_time":461.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":458.36,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Nope.","index":113,"end_time":463,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":462.44,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Two mess or an email and two LinkedIn messages and no response.","index":114,"end_time":468.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":463.8,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"She accepted the connection and we were allowed to message her.","index":115,"end_time":471.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":468.36,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So then I followed up with her on LinkedIn and she didn''t respond to that either.","index":116,"end_time":475.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":471.96,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So.","index":117,"end_time":475.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":475.48,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s so weird.","index":118,"end_time":480.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":478.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, and then I sent over the updated outreach sequence for emails.","index":119,"end_time":490.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":484.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So that''s the new sequence that we want to send for one for DSOs and then one for billing companies.","index":120,"end_time":495.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":490.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So once we have that approved, then we can create a new list of people to start sending new ABM emails to.","index":121,"end_time":502.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":496.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, so just let me know once you have feedback for those.","index":122,"end_time":505.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":503.01,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, I''ll take a look at that today.","index":123,"end_time":508.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":506.45,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay.","index":124,"end_time":509.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":509.09,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then just looking at the LinkedIn messages.","index":125,"end_time":514.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":511.49,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So for billing orgs, we have a 24% acceptance rate for the outgoing connection requests and a 67% message reply rate.","index":126,"end_time":522.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":514.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"DSO is a slightly lower 15% acceptance rate and a 26% message reply rate.","index":127,"end_time":528.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":522.62,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then yesterday I sent over the weekly website visits and email clicks.","index":128,"end_time":533.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":529.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So like we talked about last time.","index":129,"end_time":536.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":534.62,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So on the 31st we''ll do a analysis of all the clicks that happened in January.","index":130,"end_time":542.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":536.26,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we''re going to look at all the people that had three plus clicks this month and then send that list over to you.","index":131,"end_time":548.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":542.86,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then we talked about having a lower funnel nurture sequence coming from Keenan.","index":132,"end_time":553.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":548.36,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":133,"end_time":554.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":554.32,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So when you say on LinkedIn that the billing org''s 24% acceptance rate, 67% message reply rate, what messages are they replying to?","index":134,"end_time":564.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":555.12,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So either the connection message that we''re sending them or the follow up message that we send them.","index":135,"end_time":571.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":566.08,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So does that mean accepting the.","index":136,"end_time":573.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":571.84,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So the 24% if they accept the connection, that''s what that is.","index":137,"end_time":578.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":574.89,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yes.","index":138,"end_time":580.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":579.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So would I see the messages for the 67%?","index":139,"end_time":583.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":580.89,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yes.","index":140,"end_time":585.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":584.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So where, where should I be seeing that?","index":141,"end_time":588.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":587.13,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Because on LinkedIn when I look through, like I said, we have, there''d be 37 between last week and this week that have come through and I think I only have four or five people that have replied.","index":142,"end_time":601.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":588.93,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Would it be on Brad''s account?","index":143,"end_time":602.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":601.59,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":144,"end_time":603.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":603.51,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And that, that doesn''t seem like 67%.","index":145,"end_time":606.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":603.91,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"That''s where I''m confused.","index":146,"end_time":608.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":607.51,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So most of them, the only message I see is it''s the message to them.","index":147,"end_time":615.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":609.99,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I have one, 3, 4, Five, six.","index":148,"end_time":641.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":616.39,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So 7 out of 38 is what I actually see messages.","index":149,"end_time":650.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":645.6,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So if I either I''m missing something or that number might be skewed a little bit.","index":150,"end_time":656.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":650.72,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah, they should.","index":151,"end_time":659.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":658.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean they will all show up in the Messages part of LinkedIn.","index":152,"end_time":662.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":659.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":153,"end_time":663.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":662.76,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I have seven out of the 38 that I have replies from.","index":154,"end_time":666.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":663.12,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Is it so that I don''t know where that''s.","index":155,"end_time":673.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":667.4,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah, but I guess we''re looking specifically at billing.","index":156,"end_time":679.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":674.84,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Org.","index":157,"end_time":680.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":679.64,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So if that''s only a few people and a few have responded, then 67% is more likely in something like that.","index":158,"end_time":686.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":680.04,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah, it would depend on how many connection requests were actually sent out and then of those 24% were accepted.","index":159,"end_time":694.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":687.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, okay, I''ll look more through that.","index":160,"end_time":698.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":694.67,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But just.","index":161,"end_time":700.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":698.59,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"You''re looking in the right place.","index":162,"end_time":703.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":701.95,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":163,"end_time":703.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":703.23,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"There''s nothing you would be missing.","index":164,"end_time":704.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":703.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Everything, every reply that you''d receive would come into those, that message section.","index":165,"end_time":709.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":704.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":166,"end_time":710.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":709.85,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":167,"end_time":711.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":711.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"What, what are they saying?","index":168,"end_time":713.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":711.77,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"How about Ashley?","index":169,"end_time":715.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":714.41,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"This one?","index":170,"end_time":718.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":717.37,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Huh.","index":171,"end_time":719.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":718.41,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Dental intelligence.","index":172,"end_time":724.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":722.89,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We, we love dental intelligence.","index":173,"end_time":726.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":724.25,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We''re different though.","index":174,"end_time":727.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":726.29,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Maybe a question for her.","index":175,"end_time":731.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":729.85,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I, I mean, I don''t know.","index":176,"end_time":734.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":731.25,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And then Zanette what is she saying?","index":177,"end_time":740.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":738.13,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Oh, that sounds promising.","index":178,"end_time":754.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":752.45,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":179,"end_time":756.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":756.29,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Do you guys remember her?","index":180,"end_time":757.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":756.65,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Zanetta.","index":181,"end_time":761.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":760.05,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"No.","index":182,"end_time":763.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":763.3,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I mean, I meet tons of people, but that''s going to be tough for you, Keenan, because she knows who we are.","index":183,"end_time":769.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":763.94,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":184,"end_time":769.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":769.54,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"And me.","index":185,"end_time":770.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":769.94,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":186,"end_time":772.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":771.78,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"If she works, what was her.","index":187,"end_time":776.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":774.66,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Zenetta.","index":188,"end_time":777.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":776.26,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Scroll down.","index":189,"end_time":777.579,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":777.02,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And she worked for E Assist.","index":190,"end_time":778.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":777.579,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Fascinating.","index":191,"end_time":783.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":782.5,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":192,"end_time":786.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":785.94,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Fascinating.","index":193,"end_time":787.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":787.07,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s going to be a fun one for you.","index":194,"end_time":795.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":793.87,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":195,"end_time":797.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":796.83,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"But she''s in healthcare operations, so.","index":196,"end_time":802.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":800.03,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":197,"end_time":803.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":802.91,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Oh, and she''s on a revenue cycle team and she''s dealt with a grip on.","index":198,"end_time":810.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":806.27,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, she needs to.","index":199,"end_time":813.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":812.6,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"She might be a good prospect.","index":200,"end_time":814.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":813.48,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":201,"end_time":818,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":817.64,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So there''s a few in there that I''ll dig into that I think are good potential that I''m going to go ahead and message anything.","index":202,"end_time":823.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":818,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Anybody who sent a message back, I''ll respond to and then I''ll probably pick out a few others as well.","index":203,"end_time":829.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":823.56,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":204,"end_time":831.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":831,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right, and then for the website updates, the tiered onboarding, the developer just sent me a note.","index":205,"end_time":842.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":836.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Shane, they just sent the pull requests and gave those right now.","index":206,"end_time":845.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":842.66,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":207,"end_time":851.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":847.26,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then for our stats, so just across the website, stats are going down.","index":208,"end_time":856.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":852.46,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So it''s going to be important for us to get these new campaigns launched.","index":209,"end_time":860.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":857.02,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"As we''ve seen, historically, our biggest driver of website visits has been these ABM campaigns.","index":210,"end_time":867.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":861.02,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So when those start to slow down, everything else slows down too.","index":211,"end_time":871.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":868.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we should prioritize looking at those messages and then getting these new campaigns out.","index":212,"end_time":877.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":872.59,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then for our LinkedIn metrics, they''re looking healthy.","index":213,"end_time":880.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":878.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We have a strong increase in clicks and click through rate.","index":214,"end_time":883.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":880.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then we had that one conversion this month for the free trial.","index":215,"end_time":887.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":883.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":216,"end_time":893.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":892.84,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I''ve merged the marketing just now.","index":217,"end_time":895.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":893.08,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Let me do the other one.","index":218,"end_time":898.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":895.08,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":219,"end_time":898.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":898.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, and another update.","index":220,"end_time":901.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":900.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We did change the form on the website and also LinkedIn ads, so they both require phone numbers now.","index":221,"end_time":908.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":901.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, Let me check my email real quick.","index":222,"end_time":929.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":909.4,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So I want to see.","index":223,"end_time":930.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":929.33,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Right here.","index":224,"end_time":932.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":932.05,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay.","index":225,"end_time":932.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":932.57,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Both.","index":226,"end_time":933.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":932.89,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Both are updated.","index":227,"end_time":934.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":933.33,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":228,"end_time":936.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":936.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":229,"end_time":937.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":936.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So you just have the one approval list for me or is that already done?","index":230,"end_time":945.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":940.13,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yes, the.","index":231,"end_time":945.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":945.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"The outreach sequences.","index":232,"end_time":947.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":946.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I could just send it to you right after this.","index":233,"end_time":949.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":947.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Again, just so you have it at the top.","index":234,"end_time":950.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":949.23,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, perfect.","index":235,"end_time":951.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":950.95,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Where would I look for the new changes?","index":236,"end_time":954.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":952.15,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So they''re all across the different pages.","index":237,"end_time":958.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":956.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It''s like a random sentence here and there.","index":238,"end_time":960.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":958.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, got it.","index":239,"end_time":961.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":961.19,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"With the.","index":240,"end_time":962.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":961.95,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"The tiered onboarding.","index":241,"end_time":964.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":963.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":242,"end_time":967.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":964.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Maybe I''m not finding it.","index":243,"end_time":972.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":970.08,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I can send you.","index":244,"end_time":973.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":972.96,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I can send you the design files that we used, which have guided onboarding support.","index":245,"end_time":978.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":973.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Our team leads the launch and stays involved.","index":246,"end_time":980.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":978.24,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Since you''re got it.","index":247,"end_time":981.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":980.16,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"It''s on there.","index":248,"end_time":982.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":981.28,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":249,"end_time":983.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":983.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":250,"end_time":984.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":983.84,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"We updated the homepage about page, a bunch of different pages to include that.","index":251,"end_time":989.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":985.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":252,"end_time":991.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":990.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s the first thing on there.","index":253,"end_time":996.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":994.49,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Like it''s pretty high at the top.","index":254,"end_time":998.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":996.81,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So guided onboarding support our team leads launch, stays involved to ensure successful adoption.","index":255,"end_time":1004.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":998.65,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":256,"end_time":1011.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1011.21,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":257,"end_time":1014.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1013.85,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, so I will follow up with that outreach sequence, Keenan.","index":258,"end_time":1020.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1015.21,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Just for you to review and then I''ll prioritize getting these new campaigns launched.","index":259,"end_time":1024.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1020.57,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":260,"end_time":1025.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1025.33,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":261,"end_time":1027.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1026.45,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Anything else?","index":262,"end_time":1031.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1031.09,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, so I had a question.","index":263,"end_time":1034.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1033.09,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Let''s see if I can remember it.","index":264,"end_time":1035.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1034.57,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Oh, do we do monthly.","index":265,"end_time":1039.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1037.57,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Do we do the monthly newsletter still.","index":266,"end_time":1044.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1042.53,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"To prioritize points?","index":267,"end_time":1048.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1046.93,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"No.","index":268,"end_time":1048.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1048.37,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":269,"end_time":1049.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1048.77,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We don''t do that anymore.","index":270,"end_time":1050.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1049.21,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, we will have.","index":271,"end_time":1051.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1050.17,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So I wanted to let you guys know we''re about to release internal tasking and internal tasks.","index":272,"end_time":1061.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1052.75,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So right now everything goes across a team to.","index":273,"end_time":1064.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1061.91,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So biller and.","index":274,"end_time":1066.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1064.27,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And office.","index":275,"end_time":1068.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1067.31,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"That''s the back forth.","index":276,"end_time":1070.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1069.07,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Now you can task people inside your own team of billing or office.","index":277,"end_time":1073.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1070.59,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So.","index":278,"end_time":1075.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1075.31,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":279,"end_time":1077.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1077.48,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"We''ll see how well it''s received.","index":280,"end_time":1080.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1079.4,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I can measure that.","index":281,"end_time":1082.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1081,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And I''m just going to publish it at some point, probably within the next week or two and see how people gravitate to it.","index":282,"end_time":1087.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1082.04,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But anyway.","index":283,"end_time":1089.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1087.08,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":284,"end_time":1091.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1090.92,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I think the next thing.","index":285,"end_time":1093,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1091.72,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Keenan, did I mention this to you?","index":286,"end_time":1094.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1093,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I think the next thing is to potentially do online sign up just with a credit card.","index":287,"end_time":1099.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1094.68,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":288,"end_time":1103.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1102.93,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"And just make it.","index":289,"end_time":1104.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1103.17,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Make it available for them to just register themselves and.","index":290,"end_time":1106.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1104.01,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah, but.","index":291,"end_time":1107.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1106.69,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"But I really need to involve you in that because big question is, what''s our price point?","index":292,"end_time":1112.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1107.41,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Because once that price point set online, everything else is.","index":293,"end_time":1117.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1112.81,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I don''t think we''ll do discounts online.","index":294,"end_time":1119.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1117.89,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I think what we''ll do is, is have a set price, no discount per volume, and then if volume would come into you for.","index":295,"end_time":1135.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1124.29,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"For discounted tiers and then that would bypass that feature.","index":296,"end_time":1139.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1135.18,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So you wouldn''t sign up online.","index":297,"end_time":1140.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1139.3,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"So.","index":298,"end_time":1142.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1141.98,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":299,"end_time":1148.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1143.179,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Because with onboarding support advertised and they register online, the other thing to think about is then are they like, okay, schedule us, get us started and then I''m in the middle of a work trip now.","index":300,"end_time":1159.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1148.1,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"We''re trying to.","index":301,"end_time":1160.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1159.72,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"That''s why I need to stay close to you.","index":302,"end_time":1162.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1161.04,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Just because we have the feature, we need to think about what it means from a business standpoint.","index":303,"end_time":1166.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1162.56,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":304,"end_time":1167.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1166.56,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"It''s going to take a couple months to develop too, I think.","index":305,"end_time":1169.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1167.12,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay.","index":306,"end_time":1172.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1172.32,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":307,"end_time":1173.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1172.96,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Because I think potentially, I mean for what I.","index":308,"end_time":1175.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1173.36,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"For what I have now, if I''m working half day Fridays, we potentially have the option of if they register, then they get contacted that they get scheduled for that Friday for their initial launch or whatever.","index":309,"end_time":1190.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1175.76,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So whatever week they.","index":310,"end_time":1191.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1190.55,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"They register.","index":311,"end_time":1192.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1192.07,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"If we can make that a thing somehow, that might be the safest thought in my mind immediately.","index":312,"end_time":1198.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1192.83,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Let''s talk more after this.","index":313,"end_time":1199.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1198.31,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Keenan, if you''ve got a second, I''d like to strategize a little bit with you on this.","index":314,"end_time":1203.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1199.67,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay?","index":315,"end_time":1204.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1203.67,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":316,"end_time":1208.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1208.07,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":317,"end_time":1209.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1208.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So good.","index":318,"end_time":1210.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1209.19,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"What else do we have to do?","index":319,"end_time":1211.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1210.19,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Natalie, how''s our numbers looking for this for website visit chains down because we haven''t sent out a. Yeah.","index":320,"end_time":1218.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1211.47,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"As we''ve seen, like, the biggest driver of website visits historically has been the ABM campaigns.","index":321,"end_time":1224.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1219.42,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So when those slow down, everything else slows down.","index":322,"end_time":1227.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1224.62,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So.","index":323,"end_time":1227.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1227.42,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"So what I''d like us to.","index":324,"end_time":1229.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1227.82,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"My.","index":325,"end_time":1230.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1230.46,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"My days are just crazy slammed.","index":326,"end_time":1233.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1230.86,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Keenan, if you''re too busy, and I know you said you were going to look at it today, but if you are too busy, would you have any objection of them just sending it?","index":327,"end_time":1241.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1234.3,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I have time this morning.","index":328,"end_time":1245.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1244.39,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"I got back from a trip and so I''m working from home today.","index":329,"end_time":1249.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1245.99,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay.","index":330,"end_time":1250.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1249.51,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"I don''t have anything for the next hour probably, so I''m going to go ahead and look at that right after we get off and you and I have a conversation.","index":331,"end_time":1257.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1250.39,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":332,"end_time":1258.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1257.83,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"We''ll move on that then.","index":333,"end_time":1260.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1259.35,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":334,"end_time":1261.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1260.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right, I''ll send it right over.","index":335,"end_time":1263.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1262.55,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Keenan.","index":336,"end_time":1264.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1264.07,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, thank you.","index":337,"end_time":1266.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1265.03,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"},{"text":"Thanks, guys.","index":338,"end_time":1267.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1267.19,"speaker_name":"Shane Billings"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":339,"end_time":1268.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1268.07,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Appreciate it.","index":340,"end_time":1269.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1269.26,"speaker_name":"Keenan Toward"}],"dateString":"2026-01-29T13:30:00.000Z","host_email":"nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/83663022990?pwd=R1aTMdTGv2yblYfzlB6Wv1Sup4Z47U.1","participants":["colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com,david.edmund.reynolds@gmail.com,shane@agrippon.com,f.dominguez@agrippon.com,j.samstag@agrippon.com,monique.ki